window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The epic tale of everyone's favorite dark elf, Drizzt Do'Urden, reaches new heights! </p> <p>Drizzt Do'Urden struggles with his own inner voices, voices that call him back to the pitiless depths of the Underdark. But louder still are the voices of his newfound friends, and the dream that drives Bruenor Battlehammer on to reclaim Mithral Hall. Time and again they're told to turn back, that some dreams can never be fulfilled, but on they fight - together.</p>"; 
